thread.title: Mary Jones
thread.title_full: Sheenco Travel reviewed by Mary Jones

author: Mary Jones
title: Mary Jones
text: I booked my vacation in Sept 2016. Loved every moment of it. The accommodations were excellent, the car was well maintained and very efficient. The crew at Sheenco Travel were so wonderful & courteous to work with. They answered all of my question timely & professionally. Their recommendations were spot on! they know how to plan a vacation!!
